{"tid":374412,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"間間大學都有玩ocamp,做乜鳩針住我地恒大？","createTime":"2017-08-25T17:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T03:48:35.000Z","uid":33866,"like":0,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"38ef14047aa365b570a98c8d6fb14594abc23bdf","tid":374412,"uid":33866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又無阻到人， 間間大學著件camp tee大家一齊玩下，又要影影影，都唔知影乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連狗淨係識偷影，夠膽就上前屌我哋阿笨？<br />\n鍵盤戰士，我呸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c694e0107d5e1167447bff41233bf7f1531babd","tid":374412,"uid":123264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:18:07.000Z","msg":"Sor lo恆大屍兄"},{"pid":"ccd60621b33d74b51df994cb5969113a9a307277","tid":374412,"uid":33866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sor lo恆大屍兄</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊玩囉縮頭烏龜"},{"pid":"fa7d09af303a89a96782719eb4573af984c7962e","tid":374412,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:22:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Sor lo恆大屍兄</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊玩囉縮頭烏龜</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我夠班侵你玩咩"},{"pid":"26eb67aec55b6c6e